{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tabletop Tavern Demo is a RTS game designed for Roguelike enthusiasts seeking high replayability with endless combinations. In this demo you will play through the first 11 chapters of Tabletop Tavern. Recruit troops that you will then command in real-time on a battlefield set on a tabletop. Each playthrough presents unique challenges, with difficult decisions to make and ferocious enemies to encounter. Recruit a diverse roster of mercenaries, make difficult choices, discover powerful gear, and command your troops in battle against the goblin hordes.   <br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410010/extras/armies.png?t=1736977942\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Real time Battles: </strong>Command your troops on the battlefield tabletop</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410010/extras/recruit.png?t=1736977942\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Recruit:</strong> from a diverse roster of mercenaries, each with their own skills and stories, to form your company.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410010/extras/roguelike.png?t=1736977942\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Roguelike Elements:</strong> Each run is unique. Choose your path and craft a unique build by collecting powerful gear that provide bonuses to your troops. Adapt, survive, and perhaps, thrive in this unpredictable environment. </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410010/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736977942","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3410010/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736977942","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstati